## ğŸ’¡ How It Works

1. User enters a 4-digit password in Serial Monitor.
2. If correct â†’ LED ON, access granted.
3. If incorrect â†’ attempt count increases.
4. After 3 wrong tries â†’ System locks and displays a warning.

